1. *Marširajte* u koloni po dvoje! (March in columns of two!)
2. Ovaj *marš* traje tri sata. (This march lasts for three hours.)
3. *Marševi* su bili zabranjeni u toj zemlji. (Marches were prohibited in that country.)
4. *Marširali* smo kroz centar grada. (We marched through the city center.)
5. Naredili su nam da *marširamo* do kampa. (They ordered us to march to the camp.)
6. Pridružićeš nam se na *maršu* za ljudska prava? (Will you join us on the march for human rights?)
7. Žandarmerija je primenila silu protiv *marša*. (The gendarmerie used force against the march.)
8. Ova pesma je poznata kao *marš* vojske Srbije. (This song is known as the march of the Serbian army.)
9. Dizajnirali su novi *marš* za vojnike. (They designed a new march for the soldiers.)
10. *Marširajući* u tišini, mogao sam čuti zvuk svojih koraka. (Marching in silence, I could hear the sound of my footsteps.)